⁶ flffemoriam nostri] Nostri is in this place the genitive plural of the pronoun eqo. And memoria nostri has a very different significa- tion from memoria nostra. The former denotas the memory of us among postersty, the latter imports the memory or remembrance we ourselves have of predecessors, or things past.-M.
